Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.10,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.10,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.10,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:32.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnNarkisim\b0\fs48\fad(450,0)\pos(358,70)\shad3\be2\bord1.5\c&HF6F9FF&\3c&H1C74F6&\4c&H1C74F6&}Sentimental Bus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Cromartie High School's field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:37.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A bus filled with hotheaded\N badasses heads straight to Nikko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:40.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In the back of that bus,\Na man sits, holding his breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:43.37,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(351.203,393)}Yutaka Takenouchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:43.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yutaka Takenouchi, 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:47.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As the boss, I'm currently\N commanding Cromartie's Year 1 guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:49.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm an able fighter and considered reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it,\Nthere is no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:54.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I am respected even by the Year 3 guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:58.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But even I have one big problem\Nthat I am fighting against.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:00.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:04.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I get motion sickness very easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:09.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I like taking trips. I can't miss them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Especially since Nikko is my favorite place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can get immersed in an elegant feeling\Njust by looking at the antique temples.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:20.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since elementary school, I've been getting\Nthrough this hardship with spirit and guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to brag,\Nbut I've never once thrown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:26.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, look. Takenouchi looks furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Something must've really pissed him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:31.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We should really try and keep\Nour distance from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if life's easy here, you call it Cro- Cro-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:39.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ah, Cromartie is our alma mater
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can find a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:44.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's this? For some reason,\Nall the seats in the back are empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:45.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:56.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Not good! I've been doing fine\Nsince I started high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I've just made an irreparable mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What should I do? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wanna tell him "Get off, now!",\Nbut I might throw up if I open my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:08.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We are now entering Iroha Hill Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Iroha Hill Road!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just hearing the name makes me wanna hurl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:19.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've never gotten scared\N no matter how strong my opponent was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I kept winning fights one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But when I face this Iroha Hill Road,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,it still sends a chill down my spine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And how long is this guy going to sit on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm in trouble.\N I'm in seriously big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:32.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Still, it's disrespectful\N if I don't take off the hat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Get off, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please be careful, since the bus\N will rock violently from side to side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It's because the bus is rocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:48.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Right at that moment, Kamiyama's eyes\Nlooked like those of an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:52.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no mistaking it. He's after my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's true that I could be targeted at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:01.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's probably working with guys from\Nother schools, trying to destroy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:05.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But, Kamiyama, I'm not commanding\NYear 1 at Cro-High for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:09.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have enough power to\Nturn the tables on the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You look pale.\N Please pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:16.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry! You win! I'm begging you,\Nplease don't touch me any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:19.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By any chance, Takenouchi, is it that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right, it's motion sickness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.\N It's obvious that you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:30.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My apologies. I hadn't realized\Nand acted insensitively.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:35.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have something carefully\N put aside for times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:36.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please have this pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're hungry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:42.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please have my snack.\NIt's a little warm now, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's a sleeping cat, meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:49.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard that Takenouchi ate pudding\Nand then lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Pudding? What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:54.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right, let's enjoy Nikko, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yutaka Takenouchi, 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The man who commands Year 1 at Cromartie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:02.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's an able fighter and considered reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it,\Nthere is no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's respected even by the Year 3 guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,However, a guy like him still has one weakness.\NThat weakness is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:15.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He is extremely susceptible to motion sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it has nothing to do with my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Takenouchi, there's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Maeda got kidnapped \Nby guys from Bass High School!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:22.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm fundamentally opposed to fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but after all, we must do everything\Nwe can to save our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should round up some guys too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've fought with Bass High School\Nseveral times before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That school's no big whoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:36.73,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(620.835,305)\b0\shad3\bord1\be1\c&HF3F5F6&}No big whoop = One of the delinquent terms.\NIt means "no big deal"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I could handle 'em by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes! We have everything ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Here, please get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Can't we just walk over there, since it's close?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:49.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Maeda could be getting beaten up\Nby a bunch of guys right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We've got no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:57.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Not good! I don't like cabs\Nas much as I don't like tour buses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Cabs have enough power\Nto take me out in one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm getting sick just by looking at the cab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:07.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Takenouchi, get in quickly.\NThings can't start without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:14.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If people find out that I get carsick,\Nmy reputation will be devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In the worst case, I won't even be able\Nto walk around in my own neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Before we get in the car,\Nlisten to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I know that you wanna hurry up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but if we act rashly and they turn\Nthe tables on us, it won't be pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We should plan a detailed strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If possible, we should go back\Nto the classroom and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's true that it could be a trap to lure us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It may be good to plan a strategy carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You see? This is definitely a trap!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.45,0:06:38.87,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(700,0)\fs20\fnJanieHmkBold\c&HC27F47&\bord50\be2\3c&HFFFDFF&\an9\pos(186.93,334)\1a&HFF&\clip(m 86.125 326 b 99.75 324 121.25 330 141.625 329 155.25 328 167.625 329 180.125 332 189.25 336 193.75 343 193.75 353 193.75 377 173.375 382 146.125 381 125.75 381 99.75 381 89.5 374 78.125 368 65.75 362 62.25 348 63.5 334 65.75 331 75.875 327)}Good thing they\N are morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:38.87,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(700,0)\fs20\fnJanieHmkBold\c&HC27F47&\bord50\be2\an9\pos(186.93,334)\3c&H000000&\clip(m 86.125 326 b 99.75 324 121.25 330 146.125 327 160.875 327 171.125 327 182.375 331 192.625 334 196 341 197.125 353 197.125 381 174.5 384 147.25 384 125.75 383 100.875 384 89.5 376 78.125 371 62.25 363 62.25 348 63.5 334 65.75 331 75.875 327)\1a&HFF&}Good thing they\N are morons.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:35.45,0:06:38.87,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fad(700,0)\fs20\fnJanieHmkBold\c&HB88555&\bord0\blur0.4\an9\pos(186.93,334)\1c&HBA773E&}Good thing they\N are morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then let's plan a strategy first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then let's plan a strategy after we get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I ended up in the car after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and on top of that, I'm sitting in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:53.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sitting in the middle, \NI can't get fresh air, nor can I run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:58.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And who the hell's the rock singer\Nlooking guy in the passenger seat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'm getting sick thinking\Nabout unnecessary things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have to focus my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's because I can't get you guys involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:15.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you're saying at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Bass High is pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:20.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There'll probably be lots of blood spilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You said earlier that they were no big whoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:25.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'll go by myself on foot,\Nso I'm getting off! No, let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:28.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? We're all from Cromartie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:31.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When we die, we die together.\NWe'll never let you get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll die before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:35.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:41.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've moved here recently, so I don't know\Nmy way around Tokyo very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's all right if you take a little longer route.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You were saying earlier that\Nwe don't have any time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:48.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But we can't help it if he doesn't know the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:51.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Screw that! if you take a longer route\Nor something, I'll fudgin' kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Takenouchi! That's not the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Give me the map! I'll navigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:56.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&}Yes!
