Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:00.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I said I'd navigate, but if I look\Nat the map for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,there is a risk that I'll get sicker.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'd better find the shortest route quickly.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,First head south through\Nthe Scandinavian Peninsula,
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,then go through the Panama Canal,\Nand cross the international date line...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:12.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is a world map!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Russia's marked\Nas the Soviet Union!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap! Takenouchi fell unconscious again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Two hours have passed since Maeda\Nwas abducted by Bass High students.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:29.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Although they got in a cab to save\NMaeda without a moment's delay,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:32.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,because of the fluke of a driver\Nwho did not know his way around,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:35.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,a tense atmosphere prevailed in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:39.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And Takenouchi's car sickness\Nwas at its peak as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't tell them that\N I don't like cars at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:46.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If I had known this would happen, I would have\Neaten something that's easy to digest for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, why do I have to deal with all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:54.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, I don't know Maeda\N that well, and he's just a classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:57.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel sick. I want to get out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's been more than an hour\Nsince we got in the cab, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:04.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, it only takes about twenty minutes\Nto get to Bass High School, even on foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Our strategy has already failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I imagine the cab fare will be high as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We don't have any money, so we'll be\Nin trouble unless we get off soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:17.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I got a\Ncab coupon from my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:21.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then no matter how long we ride, we don't\Nhave to worry about the fare, right, Hayashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We'll be fine\N even if we rode all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:27.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Do you want to save your friend\Nor just ride around in a cab?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listening to you guys talking gets\Non my nerves! Be quiet for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:37.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The scenery outside of the window\Nis something that looks really unfamiliar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We can see the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:42.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It seems that\N we're getting close to my parents' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mr. Driver, there should be a limit\Nto not knowing your way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:47.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the heck's gonna happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:49.86,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\shad0\fs16\fnJanieHmkBold\c&HC97731&\bord0\blur0.5\3c&HFFFDFF&\an9\pos(427.108,70)}Cars rock a lot on rural roads...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, as things stand, we don't\Nhave time to worry about Maeda.
