Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Look! Freddie's looking at the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's pointing right.\N Could it be he knows the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:10:00.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see! He must be looking\N for the way with his animal instincts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mr. Driver, please go right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay.
