Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Left, this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:11.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It seems the scenery is becoming familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no mistaking it,\Nwe're getting close to the destination!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It was a long way, but we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll take my anger out on them with all my might!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:26.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Show them how dangerous Cro-High is!\NWe'll fudgin' kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:27.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
